OL,5, The new CBI boss raised concerns over  
OL,6, sexual harassment when she was in a    
OL,7, senior role at the group, she has said.
OL,9,F"Whenever I have seen sexual           
OL,10,Fharassment, I have acted and I raised  
OL,11,Fthose issues," said Rain Newton-Smith. 
OL,13,FThe revelation comes after the CBI     
OL,14,Fadmitted on Monday it hired "culturally
OL,15,Ftoxic" staff and failed to fire people 
OL,16,Fwho sexually harassed colleagues.      
OL,18,FBut Ms Newton-Smith, who has been      
OL,19,Fappointed to save the group, said she  
OL,20,Fdidn't feel there was a toxic culture. 
